Package com.redis.app.redis_app_studio.shared

package com.redis.app.redis_app_studio.shared
  • Class
    Description
    ApplicationGenerator
    Application generation class for Redis App Studio.
    AppResource
    The AppResource is responsible for managing data resources (both source and target) for the parent application.
    AppSession
    The AppSession class manages the creation and recovery of a previously created session.
    AppSession.Builder
    The Builder class provides utility methods for constructing application sessions.
    Constants
    The Constants class is responsible for centralizing the constants used throughout the application.
    Constants.DataType
     
    DataLoader
    The Data loader is responsible to loading data files from the filesystem, establishing Redis connections and bootstrapping the databases with data.
    SCDSRequest
    Collection of utility methods that support transformation of SmartClient Data Source Requests into Redis Foundational objects.
    SCDSResponse
    Collection of utility methods focused on converting Foundation objects into SmartClient response payloads.
    SCLogger
    The SmartClient logger class leverages the SmartClient logger stream for generating log messages related to data items, docs, grids and DSCriteria.
    SessionContext
    The SessionContext manages the lifecycle of a Servlet session.
